{"tid":1048330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【政壇諸事町】游蕙禎變身KOL代言產品？　","createTime":"2019-03-05T14:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T09:17:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"29f93d5c086a8f492f82b0455eb20d8e57e3d18c","tid":1048330,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2513490/org/9556560a2cb099c036b7005aa66cfcda.jpg/DX36-cvB5WCxJtPXN56FwcjQNR2pT12xVsQYNFbEGDQ?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2513490%2Forg%2F9556560a2cb099c036b7005aa66cfcda.jpg%2FDX36-cvB5WCxJtPXN56FwcjQNR2pT12xVsQYNFbEGDQ%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=92f0291a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有「政界女神」稱號的游蕙禎近日有新動向，過往喜歡在社交媒體發表政評的她，今年1月起其facebook頻頻出現護膚產品相片及介紹產品的千字文，帖文又hashtag有關品牌，令人揣測這位前立法會議員開始職涯轉型，轉戰KOL界為品牌賣廣告，倘真如是，她極可能本港成為首名轉任產品代言賺錢的女議員。<br />\n<br />\n游蕙禎今日（5日）又在instgram發帖文，推薦某瑞典品牌藍牙耳機。記者透過whatsapp向她查詢是否收費為產品代言，她僅回應：「暫時不接受訪問。」<br />\n<br />\n2016年底被「DQ」立法會議席後，青年新政梁頌恆常現身政治議題的公開場合，不過曾為「拍檔」的游蕙禎似乎行着走另一條路，除了在facebook分享相關帖文外，已甚少公開亮相，反而常更新facebook和Instagram個人專頁，題材大多與日常生活有關。<br />\n<br />\n網民發現，游蕙禎今年開始有職涯「轉型」迹象，頻於社交平台上載與護膚品及護髮素產品等相片，今(5日)亦上載一瑞典品牌的耳機相片，同時附載大量文字推介。不少網民留言問她是否要轉戰KOL界。<br />\n<br />\n游蕙禎於2016年底因宣誓風波而被取消立法會議員資格後，遭立法會追討93萬議員薪金及津貼，而她與梁頌恆不服被褫奪議席展開訴訟，由原審至上訴，一直敗訴，估計有關訟費或累積達千萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/302488/%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%87%E8%AB%B8%E4%BA%8B%E7%94%BA-%E6%B8%B8%E8%95%99%E7%A6%8E%E8%AE%8A%E8%BA%ABkol%E4%BB%A3%E8%A8%80%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81-%E6%94%BF%E7%95%8C%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E8%BD%89%E5%9E%8B%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F302488%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25A3%2587%25E8%25AB%25B8%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%2594%25BA-%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E8%2595%2599%25E7%25A6%258E%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%25BA%25ABkol%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A8%2580%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%2593%2581-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%2595%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E8%25BD%2589%25E5%259E%258B%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%259C%2589&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=3f7281c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/302488/%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%87%E8%AB%B8%E4%BA%8B%E7%94%BA-%E6%B8%B8%E8%95%99%E7%A6%8E%E8%AE%8A%E8%BA%ABkol%E4%BB%A3%E8%A8%80%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81-%E6%94%BF%E7%95%8C%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E8%BD%89%E5%9E%8B%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89</a>"},{"pid":"f51133c1da1b846fdfdcf7a9e201069f8301739b","tid":1048330,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35009ce9ec2f6f430411e82e30c2a24f5642bd0","tid":1048330,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f51133c1da1b846fdfdcf7a9e201069f8301739b","tid":1048330,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:40:58.000Z","msg":"唔著鞋更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfffa168d0f8b78f41c945dafa1d776fc9af43b","tid":1048330,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f35009ce9ec2f6f430411e82e30c2a24f5642bd0","tid":1048330,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f51133c1da1b846fdfdcf7a9e201069f8301739b","tid":1048330,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:40:58.000Z","msg":"唔著鞋更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img